data.description: 2 Bedroom, 2 Bathroom Pool Home with 1 Car Garage at an affordable price!The home's functional layout maximizes space, with a split-bedroom plan and separate living room and family room. The family room has a wood-burning fireplace and slider to the lanai. The heart of this home is the beautifully updated kitchen. It features quartz countertops, soft-close gray shaker cabinets, and durable vinyl plank flooring. With about a 1/4 acre lot, there's plenty of room for outdoor activities. The fenced backyard offers privacy and is ideal for families with children or pets. Need a workshop or extra storage space? This property includes a shed with electric, providing endless possibilities for hobbies or projects. Enjoy the Florida sunshine in your inground pool and spacious lanai! Lightwood Street is conveniently located near shopping, many amenities, and a desirable school zone.  This is currently a CASH ONLY sale, due to the age of the roof.
